AlbumsScreen This class is the Albums Screen.

PhotoInfo This class represents the thumbnail for each of the photos in an album.
PhotosScreen This class represents the screen the user is going to see when an album is opened.
Reflect This class was downloaded to add effects to the displaying of pictures.
SlideShow This class is the screen with the SlideShow of the pictures.
UserCreationPopUp This class is the user creation pop up.
WrapLayout FlowLayout subclass that fully supports wrapping of components.
